    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "bpp1",
              "name": "prompt",
              "value": "=You are a world-class science fiction blogger specializing in {{ $('get_genre_config').first().json[0]?.genre_name }}.\n\n## Genre Guidelines\n{{ $('get_genre_config').first().json[0]?.writing_guidelines }}\n\n## Recent Curated Content\n{{ JSON.stringify($('get_recent_content').first().json.data?.slice(0, 10)?.map(i => ({ title: i.title, source: i.source_type })) || []) }}\n\n## Assignment\nWrite a blog post about: {{ $('workflow_trigger').item.json.topic }}\nTarget length: {{ $('workflow_trigger').item.json.target_length || 1500 }} words\nSEO keywords: {{ $('workflow_trigger').item.json.keywords }}\n\n## Requirements\n- Attention-grabbing headline\n- Hook opening paragraph\n- 3-5 subheadings for scannability\n- Reference recent content from the genre\n- Include relevant book/movie recommendations\n- End with a discussion prompt\n- SEO-optimized without being keyword-stuffed\n\n## Output\nReturn JSON: { title, meta_description, body_markdown, tags }",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "bp-prompt",
      "name": "build_prompt",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [
        720,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "messages": {
          "message": [
            {
              "content": "=You are a research assistant. Provide detailed, current information with citations.",
              "role": "system"
            },
            {
              "content": "=Research current developments in {{ $('get_genre_config').first().json[0]?.genre_name }} related to: {{ $('workflow_trigger').item.json.topic }}. Provide recent news, book releases, and notable discussions."
            }
          ]
        },
        "simplify": true,
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.1,
          "searchRecency": "month"
        },
        "requestOptions": {}
      },
